Learner's Takeaway
DePIN is no longer "speculative hype"; it is the emerging  infrastructure backbone  for AI and the global economy. By decoupling infrastructure from centralized CapEx and turning individuals into sovereign owners, DePIN creates a resilient, efficient layer for the next generation of wireless, mapping, and compute systems. As AI agents increasingly require "agentic compute" and "spatial truth," DePIN will provide the physical foundation for a truly decentralized world.
